/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, providing a vibrant contrast to the urban setting. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades hinting at the architectural diversity of the city. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban landscapes. The sky itself is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds, adding a serene backdrop to the bustling cityscape below.
